{
  "texts": [
    "These datasets include aligned text, image, and audio data, which are critical for evaluating the model's ability to process and integrate multimodal information.The metrics chosen for evaluating the model's performance include accuracy, F1 score, and a multimodal integration index, which specifically measures the effectiveness of combining multiple modalities compared to single-modality processing.",
    "Additionally, we assess the model's ability to maintain performance consistency across modalities, an essential factor for practical applications.Baseline comparisons were made with several state-of-theart models that represent the current benchmarks in multimodal learning.",
    "These models include both single-task focused models and other hybrid multimodal models.",
    "The purpose of these comparisons is to demonstrate the improvements our modifications bring about, particularly in terms of integration efficiency and contextual understanding across different modalities.",
    "B. ResultsThe results of the experiments indicate significant improvements in the performance of the Mistral 8x7B model with the implemented modifications."
  ]
}